name: cred-rea-fish-team-stationary-point-count-surveys-at-pearl-and-hermes-reef-2004
notes: Stationary Point Counts at 4 stations at each survey site were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 9 sites at Pearl and Hermes Reef in September, 2004 from the NOAA vessel Hi'ialakai (HI04-01). Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
